description: Clinicoin is an open source, blockchain-leveraged health and wellness platform, enhanced by a token-based rewards ecosystem. It rewards community users for taking part in health, wellness, and research activities, improving their lives and the lives of others. Clinicoin doesn't simply pay users to exercise or share their health data; it connects them to a global community of people focused on their health and wellness, providing support and encouragement so people can be their best selves.
name: Clinicoin
